// 3. Changed function Collect to use require statement instead of if statement to check if the balance is sufficient and unlock time is valid.
// 4. Added transfer statement in function Collect to send the amount to the msg.sender.
// 5. Added memory keyword in function AddMessage to declare LastMsg as a memory variable.